# Summarify

Summarify is an AI-powered web application designed to generate concise summaries of long texts. This project leverages advanced natural language processing techniques to provide users with quick and accurate summaries, enhancing productivity and comprehension.

## Features

- **Text Summarization**: Automatically generate summaries from long texts.
- **User-Friendly Interface**: Simple and intuitive web interface for ease of use.
- **Customizable Settings**: Adjust the length and detail of the summaries according to user preferences.

## Usage

1. Enter the text you want to summarize in the input field.
2. Click the "AI Summary" button to generate the summary.
3. Adjust the summary length using the provided settings if needed.


